---
---
<header class="header">
    <div class="profile-info">
        <div class="header-top">
            <div class="header-photo">
                <div class="profile-pic-container">
                    <img src="/assets/image_0.jpg" alt="Simonluca Pisano" class="profile-pic" />
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="header-text">
                <h1 class="name">SIMONLUCA <span class="gradient-text">PISANO</span></h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Professionista della Ristorazione & System Administrator</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-links glass">
            <a href="mailto:simonluca.pisano@outlook.com" class="contact-item">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg>
                simonluca.pisano@outlook.com
            </a>
            <a href="tel:+41782524484" class="contact-item">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"></path></svg>
                +41 78 252 4484
            </a>
            <div class="contact-item">
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg>
                6982 Agno, Svizzera
            </div>
            <div class="contact-item highlight">
                Permesso di soggiorno: B | Patenti: A2 - B
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="bio">
            Professionista della ristorazione formato IPSSAR con esperienza completa in cucina e sala, maturata in ristoranti e hotel in Italia, Germania e Svizzera. Solido background da cuoco, mise en place e servizio, e forte operatività come barista/cameriere su caffetteria e cocktail.
        </p>
        <p class="bio-strong">Punti di forza: affidabilità nei picchi di lavoro, velocità e ordine in preparazione/servizio, versatilità nel coprire turnazioni in più reparti e adattabilità ai contesti turistici.</p>
        
        <a href="#certificati" class="jump-link">
            Visualizza i Certificati ↓
        </a>
    </div>
</header>

<style>
    .header {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
    }

    .header-top {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2rem;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .header-top {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 35% 65%;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: left;
            gap: 2rem;
        }
    }

    .header-photo {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
    }

    .profile-pic-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 320px;
        aspect-ratio: 1/1;
        border-radius: 50%;
        padding: 5px;
        background: var(--accent-gradient);
        box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    }

    .profile-pic {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 4px solid var(--bg);
    }

    .name {
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .gradient-text {
        background: var(--accent-gradient);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
    }

    .subtitle {
        font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        font-weight: 300;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .contact-links {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        padding: 1.5rem;
    }

    .contact-item {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 400;
    }

    .contact-item svg {
        color: var(--accent-1);
    }

    .highlight {
        color: var(--accent-2);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        width: 100%;
    }

    .bio {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--text-secondary);
        max-width: 900px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .bio-strong {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        font-weight: 600;
        max-width: 900px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        border-left: 3px solid var(--accent-1);
        padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    .jump-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 0.8rem 1.8rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        border-radius: 30px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        align-self: flex-start;
    }

    .jump-link:hover {
        background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
        color: var(--accent-1);
        transform: translateY(3px);
        border-color: var(--accent-1);
    }
    
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
</style>
